#. Description of the plugin
#: agnosis.php
msgid ""
"Art blooming out of oblivion. Email your art, AI polishes it, the world sees "
"it. A free, federated publishing network for independent artists."
msgstr ""
"Ọ̀nà àkúnya ọ̀wọ̀ tó ń yọ láti inú ìgbàgbé. Rán iṣẹ́ ọnà rẹ nípasẹ̀ imeeli, AI "
"yóò tún un ṣe, ayé yóò rí i. Nẹ́tíwọ́ọ̀kì ìtẹ̀jáde ọ̀fẹ́, tí a pín káàkiri fún "
"àwọn olórin olómìnira."

