msgstr ""
"A kò lè ṣí ìdìbò yíyọ kúrò — ó ṣeé ṣe kí omi mìíràn ti ń ṣiṣẹ́ fún olórin yìí "
"tẹ́lẹ̀."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:148
msgid ""
"Issue prepared and queued — it will go out over the next few cron cycles."
msgstr ""
"A ti pèsè ìtẹ̀jáde náà, a sì ti fi sí ìdúró — yóò jáde láàárín àwọn yípo cron "
"tó kàn."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:149
